{
  "id": "L02",
  "title": "Ordering at a Café",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Willkommen! In this lesson, you'll learn how to order drinks and snacks at a German café ('das Café')."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Guten Tag",
        "meaning": "Good day"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Entschuldigung",
        "meaning": "Excuse me"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L02_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "Entschuldigung",
        "phonetic": "[ɛntˈʃʊldɪɡʊŋ]",
        "tip": "The 'sch' sound is like the 'sh' in 'shoe'. The 'u' is short, like the 'oo' in 'book'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ich hätte gern...",
        "meaning": "I would like..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V01",
      "data": {
        "einen Kaffee": "a coffee"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V02",
      "data": {
        "einen Tee": "a tea"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Haben Sie...?",
        "meaning": "Do you have...?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V03",
      "data": {
        "Apfelkuchen": "apple pie"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V04",
      "data": {
        "Ja": "Yes"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V05",
      "data": {
        "Gerne": "Gladly / With pleasure"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L02_S01",
      "title": "Getting Service and Drinks",
      "setting": "You are sitting at a table in a café and want to order.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Get the waiter's attention",
          "chatbot_message": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Order a drink",
          "chatbot_message": "Guten Tag! Ja, bitte?",
          "extract_info": {
            "user_drink": "Extract the drink the user orders"
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask if they have apple pie",
          "chatbot_message": "Gerne. Einen {user_drink}. Sonst noch etwas?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Acknowledge the confirmation",
          "chatbot_message": "Ja, Apfelkuchen haben wir."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Great! The waiter has what you want. To order it, you can say 'Ich nehme...' which means 'I'll take...'"
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ich nehme...",
        "meaning": "I'll take..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V06",
      "data": {
        "ein Stück": "a piece"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Das ist alles",
        "meaning": "That is all"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Danke",
        "meaning": "Thank you"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "To ask where something is, you can use the question word 'Wo...?' which means 'Where...?'"
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V07",
      "data": {
        "Wo": "Where"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Wo sind...?",
        "meaning": "Where are...?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V08",
      "data": {
        "die Toiletten": "the toilets"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V09",
      "data": {
        "da hinten": "back there"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V10",
      "data": {
        "links": "left"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L02_S02",
      "title": "Placing the Food Order",
      "setting": "The waiter has confirmed they have apple pie. Now, place your full order.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Order the snack",
          "chatbot_message": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Confirm that's all",
          "chatbot_message": "Sehr gerne. Ein Stück Apfelkuchen. Noch etwas?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask for the toilets",
          "chatbot_message": "Okay. Kommt sofort."
        },
        {
          "title": "Acknowledge the directions",
          "chatbot_message": "Die Toiletten sind da hinten links."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Finished? To ask for the bill ('die Rechnung'), you can get the waiter's attention and say 'Die Rechnung, bitte'."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Die Rechnung, bitte",
        "meaning": "The bill, please"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Was macht das zusammen?",
        "meaning": "What does that come to?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V11",
      "data": {
        "zusammen": "together"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "To ask 'Can I...?', use the phrase 'Kann ich...?'. It's very useful for making requests."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E11",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Kann ich...?",
        "meaning": "Can I...?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V12",
      "data": {
        "mit Karte": "with a card"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V13",
      "data": {
        "zahlen": "to pay"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L02_V14",
      "data": {
        "natürlich": "of course"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L02_E12",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Kein Problem",
        "meaning": "No problem"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L02_S03",
      "title": "Paying the Bill",
      "setting": "You have finished your coffee and cake and are ready to pay.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Ask for the bill",
          "chatbot_message": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask for the total amount",
          "chatbot_message": "Ja, natürlich. Einen Moment... Hier ist die Rechnung."
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask if you can pay by card",
          "chatbot_message": "Das macht 7 Euro 50."
        },
        {
          "title": "Thank the waiter",
          "chatbot_message": "Ja, kein Problem."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}